Dear [Name],

I hope this finds you well and in good health.
My name is [Your Name], and Im looking to buy your property at [Address].
Im willing to pay you CASH and avoid the costs of selling through a real estate agent.

   *EASY to work with!
   *CASH BUYER
   *BUY AS-IS so no REPAIRS
   *CLOSE on the date of YOUR choice

Please call [Your Phone Number] today!

Would you consider an offer on 
PropertyAddress?

Call me at 123-456-7890 when
you have a chance.
